(70, 37, 'en', 'Talaat Moustafa Group', '<h2>Talaat Moustafa Group</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Talaat Moustafa Group</strong> is one of the largest real estate companies in Egypt for what it offers in the real estate world until the company has a distinguished imprint from other companies with its successful and advanced real estate projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company has expanded in the implementation of many successful real estate projects throughout Egypt and the Middle East, the company was keen to provide integrated urban communities with wonderful architectural designs by&nbsp;the most skilled engineers to show the architectural design in its finest form&nbsp;and design.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A Short Summary About&nbsp;Talaat Moustafa</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If we look at the history of <strong>Talaat Moustafa Group</strong>, we will find that the company was founded 40 years ago and it achieved during those years many remarkable and successful achievements within the real estate market. The company diversified in the implementation of its real estate projects and implemented commercial projects, administrative projects, residential projects, economic projects and made sure to deal with the middle to upper-middle classes by providing offers in special prices and payment facilities up to several years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Talaat Moustafa</strong> now owns more than 50 million square meters of land on which the largest real estate projects have been implemented, as well as projects that are still under implementation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company contributed a lot to the development of the Egyptian economy and urbanization in Egypt with its outstanding projects, so it was keen to choose the most skilled architects with sufficient experience and know-how in the field of real estate to offer a new concept of residential life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the members of the board of directors of the company, Engineer Tarek Talaat is chairman and managing director, Engineer Hisham Talaat Moustafa is the CEO and Managing Director, and Engineer Hani Talaat Moustafa is an executive member of the company with the help of experts from abroad to follow all the developments of the era and implement real estate projects that mimic the future with all its new services, facilities, and amenities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Major Projects Of Talaat Moustafa Group</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Madinaty in New Cairo.</li>\r\n	<li>Al Rehab&nbsp;New Cairo.</li>\r\n	<li>Al Rabwa Al Sheikh Zayed.</li>\r\n	<li>May Fair Al Sherouq&nbsp;City.</li>\r\n	<li>Virginia Beach North Coast.</li>\r\n	<li>Al Rawda Al Khadraa El Agamy.</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://realestate.eg/en/145-residential-in-new-administrative-capital-celia-compound-talaat-moustafa\" target=\"_blank\">Celia</a> New Capital.</li>\r\n	<li>Four Seasons Nile Plaza Cairo.</li>\r\n	<li>Four Seasons Sharm El Sheikh.</li>\r\n	<li>San Stefano Grand Plaza - Alexandria.</li>\r\n	<li>Kempinski Nile Hotel Cairo.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Talaat Moustafa Group', 'Talaat Moustafa Group is one of the largest real estate companies in Egypt for what it offers in the real estate world until the company has a distinguished imprint from other companies with its successful and advanced real estate projects.', NULL, NULL),
