(94, 49, 'en', 'Better Home', '<h2><strong>With Better Home, you&#39;ll be on your way to a better investment.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home is a giant entity in the world of real estate and urban construction, with strong foundations in advanced engineering and technical innovation, keeping pace with the spirit of modernity, which has resulted in the Better Home Group for real estate investment leading the architecture market, with a client and investor base from all corners of the earth.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Home Company</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home Real Estate Investment began operations in 1998 as a private company, specializing in real estate investment, urban development, commercial construction projects, and a sector focused on central administrative construction.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Home Real Estate Strategy</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home Real Estate Investment&#39;s future vision is to build projects that are characterized by financial investment growth and continuous economic productivity, with a goal of 15 projects, while also satisfying customers by providing after-sales services for its units and providing all-cash facilities upon payment, in addition to having many other assets. They contribute to expanding the general economy, encouraging the demand for foreign investment, and supporting the design of the state&#39;s infrastructure characteristics through structured policies to accomplish the best through individual engineering designs, and endless bundles of services and advantages.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Home Real Estate Investment Achievements</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home Real Estate has large projects with cutting-edge designs, and these real estate developments are located in the most desirable places for owners and investors,&nbsp;Where the most important projects have been established in the commercial sector, such as the Highland theme park in Sixth of October City, and others in New Cairo, specifically the Fifth Settlement, and the Mall Cityscape in both Sixth of October City and Minya Governorate, as well as the Mega Mall and Cairo Medical Center in Sixth of October City.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Cairo Business Group is involved in a variety of activities, all of which are located in the Fifth Settlement. It&#39;s worth noting that&nbsp;<a href=\"https://realestate.eg/en/listings/2437-residential-cairo-business-plaza-compound-in-new-administrative-capital?location=6&amp;compound=2437\">Cairo Business Plaza</a>&nbsp;which covers 60 acres in the Administrative Capital, and the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://realestate.eg/en/listings/150-residential-in-new-administrative-capital-midtown-sky-compound-better-home?location=6&amp;compound=150\" target=\"_blank\">Midtown Sky</a>&nbsp;Compound which is built on 122 acres, and <a href=\"https://realestate.eg/en/listings/15-residential-in-new-administrative-capital-midtown-condo-compound?location=6&amp;compound=15\" target=\"_blank\">Midtown Condo</a>&nbsp;where 60 acres have been set aside for the development of a residential project and another for the development of commercial malls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aside from its interest in establishing a health center depicted in the Cairo Medical Center, which is equipped with the most accurate and important equipment and advanced practical tools, and this is to provide the best health and medical care&nbsp;after all the&nbsp;works are completed.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Administrative offices, such as the Cairo Business Gate and the Cairo Commercial Bank headquarters, were also established to serve public services. Where all government offices, the headquarters of several banking banks, and the headquarters of large corporations and factories are located in the Administrative Capital&#39;s financial and business district.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Home Real Estate Investment Group&#39;s management structure</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This massive structure is managed by the owner of Better Home, Engineer/ Sherif Adly and Ashraf Adel who&nbsp;holds the position of General Manager, and has evolved into a creative and modern entity that contributes to the employment of thousands of professional and efficient manpower, as well as a selection of engineers and consultants, all of which have combined to create brilliance</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Home Real Estate and Stock Market</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Better Home Group has progressed at all levels, allowing it to develop and now hold a number of businesses. Amoun is a shareholder, so is&nbsp;Better Business Electronic Company,&nbsp;Better Mix Concrete Company,&nbsp;in addition to being a shareholder in the Giovanni Canned Tuna Factory, whose investments are estimated in billions; It is a good investor and a well-managed partner</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Despite these expansions, Better Home has kept quiet about its plans to join the Egyptian Stock Exchange in trading equities and bonds.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>News from the Better Home Company</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home has recently won the Distinguished Real Estate Companies Award in the year 2020, after competing against other real estate companies such as Al Morshedy and Orascom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home strives to be the best by providing a package of real investments and boosting sales in its Midtown project units with a budget of one and a half-billion dollars.&nbsp;It has also sold 30% of the units in its Midtown Sky project, making it the largest company to obtain the highest booking value for its spectacular units, and is constantly injecting money into its projects to grow its capital capacity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To pay for the contracted units in the Cairo Business Plaza project, a very flexible approach has been devised, in order to provide facilities to people who seek to buy and investors through a system of interest-free payments (installments) at the same initial purchase prices (cash),&nbsp;with the units being delivered and all of the work being completed, which demonstrates the company&#39;s understanding of optimal planning and how to delight its consumers,&nbsp;It&#39;s also worth emphasizing that they&#39;re National Development Program-eligible units that follow the sustainable healthy environment system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Better Home Real Estate Investment Group also interacts with all visitors to the Midtown Mall by sharing the ambiance of official events and holidays with them,&nbsp;transforming it into a real estate investment building marked by a spirit of love for its consumers and allowing them to feel this social warmth,&nbsp;as an efficient approach to implement the preventative steps required to combat the Corona pandemic, while offering a high degree of sanitation and disinfection</p>', 'Better Home', NULL, NULL, NULL),
