0. All of the company&#39;s residential, business, and recreational properties are available at reasonable costs and with a variety of payment options, including instalments over several years and payment in advance with instalments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11. It has a significant team of engineers, designers, and artisans that have been trained in the most effective methods.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>مشاريع شركة تبارك القابضة</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Many real estates, commercial, and service developments are owned by Tabarak Holding Company, including:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Due to the availability of all utilities, Capital East Compound, which spans 18,200 square metres and is divided into 20 residential towers in New Nasr City, is regarded as one of the most important Tabarak Holding projects.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>The <a href=\"https://realestate.eg/ar/68-residential-in-new-cairo-avenue-90-compound\" target=\"_blank\">90 Avenue Compound</a>, which spans 50 acres on 90th Street in New Cairo&#39;s Fifth Settlement, is one of the most significant real estate developments in recent years.</li>\r\n	<li>The Maadi Heights Compound is a 12-acre compound on Cairo&#39;s ring road in the Maadi district.</li>\r\n	<li>The East Capital integrated project is located in the centre of New Nasr City.</li>\r\n	<li>Gardens of Farms is a residential development aimed at people who enjoy spending time in green environments.</li>\r\n	<li>In the city of Tabarak, the Maadi Sandry luxury project is located.</li>\r\n	<li>The Fantasia project at Ras Sidr, which is situated on a 1200 metre long beach.</li>\r\n	<li>Riyadh, Saudi Arabia&#39;s Aali Complex.</li>\r\n	<li>The Tabarak Metropolis project is located on the ring road of Maadi&#39;s new city.</li>\r\n	<li>The Aaaly Clinics project boasts a stunning panoramic view.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Tabarak Holding Company for Real Estate Investment</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tabarak Holding for Real Estate Investment is the Middle East&#39;s largest real estate investment company because it meets all of the needs of clients who want their housing units to be finished to the highest standards in terms of finishes, decorations, designs, and services, and to be delivered in instalments over a long period of time, unlike other real estate companies.</p>', 'Tabarak', NULL, NULL, NULL),
