menities, all visitors will have a spectacular view of the Green River region, which is the longest central park.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A shopping mall with the largest number of shops, restaurants, and cafes will be built, with a total of 200 commercial units, in order to provide maximum entertainment for visitors and owners, with units allocated for practicing medical activities, such as clinics and medical centers, and others for various administrative activities, such as head offices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A total of 26,000 square meters has been set aside for the benefit of Plaza Gardens for Real Estate Investment, in order to build residential towers that can compete with global skyscrapers and set a new record for the construction of the tallest residential tower in the New Administrative Capital. All necessary amenities and services, as well as a stunning green plant cover, are linked to the two towers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plaza Gardens for Real Estate Investment plans to expand and break into the new Al Alamein area, a highly developed area that is experiencing tremendous urban progress, by establishing an integrated project that includes tourism, commercial, and residential activities, and a plot of land with a total area of 133 acres has been chosen.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The most recent economic news</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Plaza Gardens for Real Estate Investment is constantly pouring these massive investments and cash, especially after a time of stagnation in the real estate market due to the Corona epidemic, to rebound triumphantly with a sales volume of $150 million.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In its Rhodes residential project, it has begun the implementation of activities and construction of 42 structures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://realestate.eg/en/18-residential-in-new-administrative-capital-Rhodes-compound\" target=\"_blank\">Rhodes Compound</a> New Administrative Capital project has completed the installation of 1500 housing units.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Payment of monetary value in return for land allocation, as it has just done with the second installment of its projects in the Administrative Capital.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plaza Gardens for Real Estate Investment was given the title of a most efficient survivor because it was one of the 60%&nbsp; of companies that applied for approval of plots of land inside the capital, and it won the lion&#39;s share of the applicants and the preferences of those in charge of developing and establishing the new capital.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Plaza Gardens Company headquarters</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The plaza gardens are located on Haram Street, adjacent to the official offices of NBE Bank, Egypt&#39;s National Bank, Giza Governorate.</p>', 'Plaza Gardens', NULL, NULL, NULL),
